----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
HEADER SIDEBAR COMPONENT
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Mobile sidebar navigation. Second-level panels use accordion-disclosure.
When an accordion opens, its matched mega_menu_item_promo block data is shown
below the nested links: promo images (with absolute title labels) + CTA button.
Matching is done by comparing sub_link.handle to block.settings.menu_item_handle.

